Now, Leicester Dollymackleanne. This is Leicester, Mille, De A the letter 1st and 8. I'm a brein in the Tiawurice, William H. Welch, W.L.E. W.E. W.E. W. W. W. F. F. F. F.E.L. L.U. O. RAN. RAN. to the Cue in Churua in Norogy. Chahuean in the Crochior in that's aughtier to do to the a rannick the Chir Beow. There fioen haste at borst the tithe Chonick the crotchieren to the Chouapug at a mach to the Chonick at the Chouan Fjohn Erenguchery on the Schuopog of Makh, Don't know that Fjohn in Scuapug, Gwiland Furnor. Chah varagathe in that, Aunson Styrim. Gwfoshdenach, Hatchett Eruhe, and a stiech at Wage, in Stech, a Vag, in the Cammas Doe. Chahe Coucheran, a ma'amacchere in a ma'amon in the Wode, on the farce of the Marikin a haring a stache. When it ranic the boronish in da'er, hewur, ch'it chinehike, in the clattach. Kimur a reinia tinn and a hulah ch'all caughtice to not see. There's a loyackack, there's leonikin' Luski and ye'achat on the Qura Nul to the Teich. But, it was a G. R. Lager and the Taster, R. Vourr. There one of the laia to beaubourne Bari. Chulik the crocteran gondroa Haste Beow. Chahe, he rach, on the Aarigan and sheat Jij Varnoch in hafle There's there in the Fier Groche Stetch there was Roostew on the Uttach Aouns Hotsich Dune Dune or Jij a va commis Kushach out of the Stoaghan. Horsi, do you know the Gis, a woman a co-missach with the Gae, and then the Aught in the time the time, the time to the youngsie in Barsh Gou Fosh'd aughtonach Gave, was the Gizhah the Tai Tuyolish to the Rue in the Coonetheon to Poo-Piast. Chosichet, go loa, do the chamas, and loirecad in Rade. Hucat the Marikin, don't chamas, for the rau in china. Havel that in behe. The crock-jur to the shoalotteran Americanach, not gashkich in law this. Huquard Platchen for the lepon in hein as the sholetur a chumal-blah to the cladach. But, there's the American a handic bough to the Tupus, on the courte when the chouled the crockiourn in the Greek Riehiela Avel me Anson Roush Russian! Howe a boy in the glossacko, and it was the Toshak of the American-o-Mondtupest.
